column5: In case someone may benefit from this sale, canadian tire is giving away $50 dollar gift card if you spend over $200. That deal in only for today 04/21/2016.check the flyer online  Enjoy!
great post, just nailed my son-in-law for the $50.00 who is a GM at a CT dealership.  He sold me a shed two hours ago.
